OL,3,CTwo tidal energy generators could be
OL,4,Ctested in Alderney waters
OL,6,FTwo new tidal energy generators could
OL,7,Fbe trialled in 's waters.
OL,9,FSpiralis Energy has approached the and
OL,10,Fthe island's Harbour Office to seek
OL,11,Fpermission to test their new
OL,12,Ftechnology.
OL,14,FThe device will not create usable
OL,15,Fenergy during the trial, but will test
OL,16,Fits potential in the island's strong
OL,17,Ftidal flow during the winter months.
