OL,3,CTwo tidal energy generators could be
OL,4,Ctested in Alderney waters
OL,6,FAlderney's Policy and Finance
OL,7,FCommittee (PFC) has confirmed its
OL,8,Fsupport in principle but has asked the
OL,9,Fcompany for a detailed presentation
OL,10,Fbefore coming to a decision.
OL,12,FPFC Chairman Nigel Vooght says: "This
OL,13,Fis an opportunity for Alderney to use
OL,14,Fa small part of its tidal resources to
OL,15,Fshow that Alderney is open for
OL,16,Fbusiness as a tidal energy test site."
