OL,3,CTwo tidal energy generators could be
OL,4,Ctested in Alderney waters
OL,6,FChief Executive of Spiralis Energy,
OL,7,FGuy Levene says: "We like the idea of
OL,8,Fsorting out or helping Alderney remove
OL,9,F1.5 million litres of diesel that they
OL,10,Fuse for their generators. But that
OL,11,Fdecision is Alderney's at the moment.
OL,12,FWe are simply talking to Alderney to
OL,13,Fuse the water as a test location.
OL,15,F"If the system works, Alderney may
OL,16,Fwell come to us and say, look, how can
OL,17,Fwe, you know, how can we connect this
OL,18,Finto our system?
