OL,3,CTwo tidal energy generators could be
OL,4,Ctested in Alderney waters
OL,6,F"It's one of the problems they've got,
OL,7,Fwhich we know they're currently trying
OL,8,Fto address, but again, this is not for
OL,9,Fus to decide on that. It's for it's
OL,10,Ffor Alderney."
OL,12,FThe proposal is asking for two of the
OL,13,Fpower-generating screws to be mounted
OL,14,Fon a floating platform in Alderney.
OL,16,FThe 'Axial Skelter' is made from
OL,17,Frecycled plastic, only uses one moving
OL,18,Fpart, and can be repaired locally with
OL,19,F3D printed parts.
