OL,4,Ctested in Alderney waters
OL,6,FSpiralis Energy will not be seeking
OL,7,Ffinancial aid from the States, who
OL,8,Fwill instead consider a fee for the
OL,9,Fuse of Alderney's waters for a maximum
OL,10,Fof 12 months.
OL,12,FThe States of Alderney hopes the trial
OL,13,Fcould lead to "economic opportunities
OL,14,Fand an additional source of renewable
OL,15,Fenergy for Alderney".
